Technical Details:
- resize_guyot_dataset.py: Batch processing tool for dataset preparation
- Image resizing: cv2.resize with INTER_AREA interpolation (best for downsampling)
- Coordinate scaling: Proportional rescaling preserves annotation accuracy
- File structure: Maintains original naming convention

Tested Results:
- Input: 5 images (14MB total, 4032x3024 resolution)
- Output: 5 images (2MB total, 1008x756 resolution at 0.25 scale)
- All 5 image-annotation pairs processed successfully
- Visualization confirmed correct coordinate scaling

Performance:
- Processing time: ~1 second for 5 images
- Compression ratio: 7:1 (14MB to 2MB)
